data.title: U.S. District Court, District of Oregon
data.meta_description: U.S. District Court, District of Oregon | 246 followers on LinkedIn. The U.S. District Court for the District of Oregon is a federal court serving the area corresponding to the state of Oregon. The District has courthouses in Portland, Eugene, Medford, and Pendleton.
